description:
We are pleased to present 1/34 Adelaide Street, Oxley Park bought to you by award winning agent Peter Diamantidis.

This modern 3 bedroom spacious brick villa property has everything needed to call a place home and conveniently located in a quiet complex at the front of the complex.

Situated close to all amenities, local schools , childcare centres, public transport and a short drive to the new St Marys stations which is soon be a metro stop for the new Airport currently under construction. This rare property is on not to be missed.

WHAT WE LOVE ABOUT THIS PROPERTY :
- 3 spacious bedrooms with built in robes and fans
- Renovated kitchen and bathroom
- Timber flooring throughout
- Downlights throughout
- Lock up garage with internal access
- Timber deck with outdoor alfresco area
- 2nd toilet in the laundry
- Low maintenance backyard.
- Close to St Marys train stations

For more information or if you would like to book a private inspection please contact Peter Diamantidis on 0404 051 702 or Jake Borg on 0423 152 217.
